des:
This skill will let you know about some technical facts. It will be used to enhance your tech knowledge.
you can open this skill by using some of the utterances like: "tell me about tech", "tell me a fact", "tell me something", " get a new fact" or you can also be able to open this skill by just say "Alexa open tech facts" ,"Alexa start tech facts" or "Tell me about tech facts".
